	<Title>
		Fat grams: How to track your dietary fat
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Tracking fat grams is an easy way to see much fat you&apos;re eating.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		To monitor how much fat I eat each day, which should I focus on &amp;mdash; fat grams, fat calories or fat percentages?
	</Question>
